{"id": "1511535447933718549", "channel_id": "1511535447933718549", "author_id": "524956633843892224", "author_name": "doudou4ji3", "content": "因為沙耶入坑  所以買了個號 \n\n希望能穩定挑戰融災400\n\n目前已經把首儲全部買過一輪 想請問目前組隊有辦法打400分嗎 或是之後如果要繼續投資角色最終法則 選誰會比較好", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T01:02:13.758000+00:00", "thread_id": "1511535447933718549", "attachments": [{"id": "1511535448327979018", "filename": "IMG_0957.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1537720, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1511535447933718549/1511535448327979018/IMG_0957.png?ex=6a217755&is=6a2025d5&hm=9792989e5076ffa37050b2fdcc9ccded80b166889ca5bc781c77c5d688edf395&"}, {"id": "1511535449552851154", "filename": "IMG_0956.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1571657, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1511535447933718549/1511535449552851154/IMG_0956.png?ex=6a217756&is=6a2025d6&hm=50577bcf14be70bb4edb30cd4d44098366ab41e8d010b496f9f871c22fce3279&"}, {"id": "1511535450261819492", "filename": "IMG_0955.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1558723, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1511535447933718549/1511535450261819492/IMG_0955.png?ex=6a217756&is=6a2025d6&hm=96c0caeb923811993d6f27e4dab94008c7dcf53b3823d977c9382b81a63c074f&"}]}
{"id": "1511697804333027400", "channel_id": "1511535447933718549", "author_id": "357866427421687818", "author_name": "passerbycat", "content": "如果只是融災400的話\n應該不用最終法則(每個最終法則值兩個+4超限)\n隊伍上我是推薦\n1. 神國(誕墨 圖魯 米粒 鯊魚)\n2. 塔薇 二四 環拉 混沌生存位\n3. 茉夏 希洛 艾繼絲 羊媽\n4. 阿拉克涅 詹金 哈姆林 朵爾\n5. 鳥哥 鳥弟 醫生 小玫瑰\n\n當然可能有更好的組隊\n但你有誕墨有塔薇有茉夏有阿拉克涅有鳥哥鳥弟\n400應該很輕鬆\n（徐 融朵 船長練度也都不低）", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T11:47:22.540000+00:00", "thread_id": "1511535447933718549", "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
